members.name: MediaKeyMessageEvent()
members.description: Creates a new instance of MediaKeyMessageEvent.

parameters.name: typeArg
parameters.description: A DOMString containing one of May be one of license-request, license-renewal, license-renewal, or individualization-request.

parameters.name: options
parameters.description: Options are as follows: messageType: A developer-defined message type that allows applications to differentiate messages without parsing them. message: An array containing the message generated by the content decryption module.

members.name: MediaKeyMessageEvent.message
members.description: Returns an ArrayBuffer with a message from the content decryption module. Messages vary by key system.

members.name: MediaKeyMessageEvent.messageType
members.description: Indicates the type of message. May be one of license-request, license-renewal, license-renewal, or individualization-request.
